# Threshold-40 reveal (M4). Single internal-voice beat fired once,
# the next time the player enters a door-knock conversation after
# doubt first crosses the ambiguous threshold (40).
#
# door_knock.gd::_start_dialogue_for_pending_house consumes
# DoubtMeter.consume_reveal_40() before starting the householder
# timeline; if true, this plays first, then chains into the
# householder timeline via Dialogic.timeline_ended.
#
# Per GDD § 5.2: "a faint, ambiguous indicator appears (a recurring
# dream, a phrase that catches on rereading, a flicker in dialogue)."
# Per CLAUDE.md § Common Pitfalls: hidden until 40, single beat.
# No character joined — the line appears with no name label, no
# portrait. Default Dialogic text-box fade-in/out.
#
# AUTHENTICITY CHECK PENDING — content review at post-M4 playtest.
# Tunable alongside N=25 calibration once Andrew has played the
# actual ramp once or twice.

A second on the porch you don't remember being there before.
